LogicalColumn.name: Order Number
LogicalColumn.Description: Credit Card Name (values based on LOV type 'PAY_ACCNT_CD')

LogicalColumn.name: Active Flag
LogicalColumn.Description: Credit Card Name Language Independent Code (values based on LOV type 'PAY_ACCNT_CD')

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IS NULL OR "%1" <= 250000 THEN 'A: 0 - 250K' WHEN "%1" <= 1000000 THEN 'B: 250K - 1M' ELSE 'C: 1M+' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Order Revenue" IS NULL OR "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Order Revenue" <= 250000 THEN 'A: 0 - 250K' WHEN "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Order Revenue" <= 1000000 THEN 'B: 250K - 1M' ELSE 'C: 1M+' END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: INDEXCOL( VALUEOF(NQ_SESSION."HIER_LEVEL"), "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Base Level Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 1 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 2 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 3 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 4 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 5 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 6 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 7 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Level 8 Current Login", "Marketing Contact List"."Dim - Order"."Top Level Current Login")

LogicalColumn.name: Frequency
LogicalColumn.Description: Order Frequency - This will often be monthly, quarterly, half yearly or annually

LogicalColumn.name: Payment Count
LogicalColumn.Description: Number of Payments for an order

LogicalColumn.name: Cancellation Source
LogicalColumn.Description: Campaign reference for order cancellation (most will be upgrade campaigns)

LogicalColumn.name: Order Source Code
LogicalColumn.Description: Campaign source code of an order

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" = 'Y' AND "%2" = 'N' AND "%3" = 'N' THEN 'CoG:Not Gift Aidable' WHEN "%1" = 'Y' AND "%3" = 'Y' THEN 'CoG:Gift Aided' WHEN "%1" = 'Y' AND "%2" = 'Y' AND "%3" = 'N' THEN 'CoG:Gift Aidable' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_FLG" = 'Y' AND "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_ORDER_MD"."X_SRM_GIFT_AID_FLG" = 'N' AND "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_GIFT_AIDED_FLG" = 'N' THEN 'CoG:Not Gift Aidable' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_FLG" = 'Y' AND "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_GIFT_AIDED_FLG" = 'Y' THEN 'CoG:Gift Aided' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_FLG" = 'Y' AND "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_ORDER_MD"."X_SRM_GIFT_AID_FLG" = 'Y' AND "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_GIFT_AIDED_FLG" = 'N' THEN 'CoG:Gift Aidable' END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 24 THEN '0-23.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 36 THEN '24-35.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 48 THEN '36-47.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 60 THEN '48-59.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 96 THEN '60-95.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 120 THEN '96-119.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 240 THEN '120-239.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" < 360 THEN '240-359.99' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."SRM List Export Tables"."Fact_W_ORDER_F"."X_SRM_COG_ANNUAL" >= 360 THEN '360+' END
